§ D118 (cssl-spectral-render / KAN-BRDF) :
    crate emits MicroColor (3-band tint) into AmplifiedFragment ;
    D118's BRDF M-coord pre-shift consumes this as additive-tint per
    07_KAN_RUNTIME_SHADING § VIII iridescence-variant.
